Author: pomp-and-regrets
Text: This happens to me when I restrict. I love feeling hungry and empty. I know that not eating will kill me in the end. But I can't seem to connect those two points, that my empty stomach is bad and will kill me. It just doesn't click and I go on with my day. It feels a bit like dissociation, but I'm just always so pleased with feeling empty that I don't want to fix the problem
